{
  "stem": "9558.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he told me that he got in touch with them, and that my wife is there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, give them a message to tell my wife that I'm alive, that I'm in Brunnlitz, and that I am OK, that I have everything.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was, but I didn't-- I didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no food there to hide.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was only five people, and I was the sixth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were [NON-ENGLISH], what they had food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the people what worked mostly were Polish people working in the kitchen, you know, but whoever worked in the kitchen had food.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But-- --I'll go back to 19, before, to Wisnicz Nowy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was privileged to have a blessing from the Belzer rebbe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a dynasty, [NON-ENGLISH], and he was a [NON-ENGLISH] as well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the Belzer rebbe came in to Wisnicz from wherever he was, because it was that time, Wisnicz, a lot of people from Krakow, from all over, they came because we lived in the houses.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And let's say whoever had the house with two rooms or three rooms had to take in-- you know, if you had three rooms, you had to take in eight people, for instance.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I give a number.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But, you know, it has to be three, four-- three, four persons in the room.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Till 1942, because in Krakow, the ghetto was already in '41.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So people run away from there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came to Wisnicz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Bochnia, the ghetto was, so they run away from there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They came-- [INAUDIBLE] not to live in the ghetto, so they came to Wisnicz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Belzer rebbe came, and I was-- I had the privilege to come to get a blessing from him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember like today.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
